{"tid":1786482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賄匯豐職員稱北京文化 前女兵判囚","createTime":"2019-12-17T07:33:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T08:15:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6f94675574409decf924415e30684c5a93454725","tid":1786482,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191217/RHTSPEZI6UOIU37G6JE6WSW3NU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191217%2FRHTSPEZI6UOIU37G6JE6WSW3NU%2F&d=oGSqBYpvdEZZERTBUGrA0itC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=08aabfac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191217%2FRHTSPEZI6UOIU37G6JE6WSW3NU%2F&h=3b041203\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191217/RHTSPEZI6UOIU37G6JE6WSW3NU/</a><br />\n<br />\n賄匯豐職員稱北京文化 前女兵判囚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191217/large/1576513857_7991.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191217%2Flarge%2F1576513857_7991.jpg&h=651c87ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九龍城法院<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】內地漢偕妻來港，欲替名下財務公司開設銀行戶口。其間退休前擔任解放軍後勤人員的妻子，在匯豐銀行男職員枱底遺下一隻「解放軍限量版」手錶，及後更向職員表明是小禮物。涉案妻子早前承認向代理人提供利益罪，求情指送禮一向是北京文化，她只是用了錯誤方式向職員表達誠意。她最終被判入獄兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n女被告馬振蓮（61歲）判刑時一直站在犯人欄內抽泣。其丈夫韓先利（67歲）早前獲控方不提證供起訴，昨亦有到庭支持妻子。韓是香港匯霖國際財務集團有限公司的獨資股東兼董事。<br />\n贈解放軍限量版錶<br />\n<br />\n辯方早前透露，被告退休前為解放軍後勤部隊人員。辯方昨呈上村委會的信件，內容指被告是虔誠的基督徒，曾為汶川大地震捐款。<br />\n<br />\n求情續指，被告於內地沒有犯罪紀錄，在丈夫的公司中亦無角色，案發當日只是陪同丈夫來港開設戶口。<br />\n<br />\n辯方又引述醫療報告，指被告心臟有問題，在香港卻「無人無物」，家人難以每星期從內地來香港探監，希望法庭判處緩刑。<br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官嚴舜儀判刑指，被告顯然有預謀犯案，儘管銀行職員已再三表明不能收禮物，被告仍堅持送「解放軍限量版」手錶，目的只為開設戶口處理巨額資金周轉。嚴官考慮到被告因身體問題而需居於羈留病房等因素，判她入獄兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC2669/19<br />\n■記者廖希呈"},{"pid":"79e5bcbc019fce535e6e627ee90e909dfa9c5248","tid":1786482,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pie4mpm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPie4mpm.jpg&h=4cc5750a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RU8EhU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRU8EhU3.jpg&h=c3f3defe&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cfadae154946e09b7dc616cfdf825c67de91329","tid":1786482,"uid":134942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"錢就話啫畀隻閪錶我做乜鳩"},{"pid":"e7c55290825f14a0d924fc694f8db19316af36e8","tid":1786482,"uid":298386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"晚有香港人道災難哀悼會無人講？！！！！(已有不反)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786309</a><br />\n<br />\n今晩要人啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3f04366f735fd591df54311d0cc6525e4c450a","tid":1786482,"uid":104804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:37:11.000Z","msg":"北京文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c0cab88eb2731614207fa8a0752b9766b03fcd1","tid":1786482,"uid":242998,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"送隻勞都話，爛鬼老解表有撚用咩"},{"pid":"3db01ebd98c4ca8bb9